        "Create the Battlefield",
        "Determine Attacker and Defender",
        "Declare Battle Formations",
        "Deploy Armies",
        "Determine First Turn",
        "Resolve Pre-battle Rules",
        "Begin the Battle",
        "End the Battle",
        "Determine Victor"
